                                <p>Tumaini Senior Secondary School offers various services to all people in the school campus. The services offered varies from one group to another. For instance, the services offered to teachers are different to those offered to students/learners. The following are some of the services offered in Tumaini Senior Secondary school may include:</p>

                                <p>Food Supply For every organism to survive, food supply is a necessary service. In Tumaini Senior Secondary School, The food is provided basing on the groups also. There are groups of people who have health problems, so the food they eat differs from those who don't have health problems. In Tumaini Senior Secondary School, There are no classes between poor and rich, so all people get equal share of food.</p>
                                <p>Water Supply, Water is much available. This is because the importance of water is well known. Something to know is that Tumaini Senior Secondary School does not depend on water from Makuyuni village instead water in Tumaini Senior Secondary School is drilled from underground. All this has come into control due to availability of electricity and power system.</p>

                                <p>Electricity Supply, when one passes around Tumaini Senior Secondary School campus during the night, the person can think maybe it's a town but in reality it is a school. This is because of proper lighting system all over the school. In Tumaini Senior Secondary School, There is a well-managed supply of electricity. The Electricity is used to operate various activities in the school like pumping of water from underground and other including lighting system. Electricity supplied in Tumaini Senior Secondary School enhance the improvement of security all over the environment.</p>

                                <p>Health Service, A student or a worker in Tumaini Senior Secondary School can never regret to be at this place. This is because good health services and good care to all people. The Good of this is that the school is located near to the Makuyuni dispensary where students can go for health checkup in case of inconveniences. Tumaini Senior Secondary School has a well-trained and educated nurse who can take care of the studentsâ€™ health all the time when they are in the school area.</p>

                                <p>Transportation, The School has a good transportation system. This roads all around the school are in a very good condition. The school also has school buses that transport both workers and students. Also the school has emergency vehicles that help to transport students to early dispensary or even big hospitals in case of serious injuries or health problems.</p>

                                <p>Hospilality, In Tumaini Senior Secondary School, Students have a very conducive environment to rest after being active for about 16hours to bed. There are very quality dormitories with good arrangement of luggage and beds. Also there is proper lighting system to ensure security of the students. During the night hours, the dormitories are guarded by security guards to secure the lives of the students.</p>
                                 <div class="cor-mid-img">
