                                <p>Religuos Services, Tumaini Senior Secondary School support both religion that prevent in Tanzania. Tumaini Senior supports Christian and Muslims and both attend their area of worship on the planned the day in which on For Christian attend on Sunday an Muslims attend on Friday, For the Muslims go to mosque and worship every Friday.</p>

